data.title: Clark Eno Orchestra
data.meta_description: At Clark Eno Orchestra, we specialize in providing exquisite musical experiences for weddings, corporate events, and more. Discover our exceptional service.
data.text:
Experience the best in live dance music! With a repertoire for all ages and musical tastes, our world-class musicians and vocalists will keep the dance floor jumpin’ all night. Playing a wide range of genres: Rock & Pop, Swing, Motown, including hits from the 70s, 80s, 90s and 2000's, this band will deliver a high energy performance that you and your guests will

be talking about for years!

The Clark Eno Orchestra is led by composer/drummer Clark Eno, If you're looking for high energy dance music, look no further! Dancing is the sign of a successful event and Mr. Eno's ensembles have been selected to perform at high profile events including First Night Manhattan at Lincoln Center's NY State Theater and The Midsummer Night Swing Series at Lincoln Center on several occasions. The band was chosen to perform at the 80th birthday party of dance legend Frankie Manning, the originator of the Lindy Hop. The orchestra has graced the stage of the Bushnell Theater on 9 separate occasions.

Mr. Eno’s compositions have been featured on TV and radio. His songs Come Out Swinging and King of Swing have been part of Major League Baseball’s All Star Game and Home Run Derby for decades.
